{"_path":"/councilor/service/s3017","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"改善 文化一路/華亞二路 專用待轉車道","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s3017-1.jpeg","sequence":3017,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/17uRXXhpih/","author":"孫韻璇","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"孫韻璇"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-12-11T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"改善-文化一路華亞二路-專用待轉車道"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善 文化一路/華亞二路 專用待轉車道"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"近期收到許多民眾反映：文化一路往林口方向待轉華亞二路的待轉格只能容納三、四台機車，但早上上班時間車流量十分龐大，大多數的車輛只能排在停止線後面 😡"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n因為待轉格過小 ，上班時機車太多，導致排超過停止線的‘’待轉‘’騎士 闖紅燈遭警方開單闖紅燈。\n服務處立即與交通局研議「設置待轉專用車道」及「增加專用時相號誌」，以保障機車族行車安全第一。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s3017-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s3017-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"改善-文化一路華亞二路-專用待轉車道","depth":2,"text":"改善 文化一路/華亞二路 專用待轉車道"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s3017.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s3017.md","_extension":"md"}